column4: 4" x 4" Wonderfully painted details make this holiday something special to enjoy. Made by Jean Mary Pierre.
8.5" x 14" Serpentine design details adorn this simple cross. Crafted by Luckson Thenor.
23" x 23" These three graceful fish seem to swim in lovely circular harmony … very unique piece! Designed and made by Meca Robertson.
5" x 5" Not just for the holidays, but every day. This new ornament is wonderfullly crafted and painted by Omiscar Luis Juste.
4" x 3" Graceful and expressive, this ornament is painted white with gold highlights. Made by Roosevelt Beauchard.
23" x 23" This unique painted sun face creation loves to show its true colors … distinctly different. Made and painted by Roosevelt Beauchard.
17" x 13.5" x 1" This new standing nativity is unique and easy to display … lovely details! Crafted by A. Augusto.
6" x 8" These bees are no mis-stake ... sold as a set of two opposing bees, these garden stakes are all the buzz! Created by Jean Sylvionel Brutus.
15" x 15" Softly colored hand-painted details adorn this wonderful medium-sized metal art creation. Made by Stanley Brutus.
11" x 11" These three buttlerflies seem to literally fly off the wall and into your heart. Crafted by Stanley Brutus.
23" x 23" The lively sun face's rays bend gracefully to form a petal appearance … the sunniest of all flowers! Designed and made by Lindor.
12" x 12" Wonderfully painted details in subtle colorations … and a great size for any space. Hand made by Mucci.
4" x 4" This white painted ornamen with gold highlights is all you need. Made by Roosevelt Beauchard.
